Ingredients
Risotto rice

Onion - finely chopped
Zucchini
Celery
Asparagus
Peas

Vegetable stock

Butter
Olive oil
Parmesan cheese

White wine




Method
Add butter and olive oil
Sauté the onions and celery
Wash with white wine
Add vegetable stock little by little
Add zuchini, asparagus
Reduce flame and keep stirring
Add peas
Add more stock little by little
Keep going till rice is almost done
Add Parmesan cheese and butter
Add zest of lemon
Add finely chopped mint leaves 
Add vegetable stock to moisten




